        <div class="panel-body">
            <pre>
                <code class="language-cpp">
                    bool DFSFind(Graph G, int v, InfoType *c){
                        bool flag = false;
                        visited[v] = true;
                        if(G.vertices[v].data == *c){
                            flag = true;
                        }else{
                            for(w = FirstAdjVex(G, v); w >= 0; w = NextAdjVex(G, v, w)){
                                if (!visited[w])
                                {
                                    flag = DFSFind(G, w ,c);
                                }
                            }
                        }
                        return flag;
                    }
                </code>
